de.dixti.jarscan
Class Result

java.lang.Object
  de.dixti.jarscan.Result

public class Result
extends java.lang.Object

A Result is a tree of Results. That means the root of the tree is a Result and every leave is a Result. A Result can represent the root, an archive or a simple file. Simple files do not have children.
JarScan creates a Result for every archive, also nested archives if the -r option is set. Jarscan only creates a Result for a simple file if it is a hit.
